data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. NO FLOOD INSURANCE NEEDED (has an elevation certificate)!!! Beautiful home in the sought after deed restricted community of Deep Creek in Punta Gorda. This 4/2/2 home has great curb appeal as soon as you drive up. Located on a small cul-de-sac, this home has mature landscaping and a new roof. Upon walking into the front entry you will see a beautiful tile throughout. The vaulted large living & dining area makes entertaining easy. The kitchen features newer stainless steel appliances, pantry and also has an breakfast area.  All the bedrooms are spread out for privacy.  The primary bedroom room has a large walk in closet and en suite bath.  2 guest rooms have a bathroom in between each room.  The 4th bedroom or den have french doors and a good size closet.   Going out the single french door to a screened in lanai area is breathtaking. Florida living at its best. The lanai has ample room for furniture to watch the wildlife out into the freshwater canal. This home is completely protected with hurricane shutters.  The garage is insulated with a mini split AC system for all your "honey do projects" and has epoxy floors, pull down attic ladder & hurricane garage door. Located in the heart of Deep Creek this home is conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, I75 and within minutes of the Punta Gorda airport. Deep Creek golf course and marina are nearby.  SELLER IS MOTIVATED!
